                <div id="collapse2" class="collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading2">
                    <div class="panel-body px-3 mb-4">
                        It depends on the banks. There are two use cases as follows:<br />
                        - For banks that offer instant transfer, funds arrive in your account in a matter of seconds (10 seconds max).<br />
                        - For banks that do not offer instant transfer yet, the funds arrive in your bank account within 48 business hours.<br />
                        In both cases, the PrestaShop module informs you of the status and condition of your payment.
                    </div>
